Chef Wanted with Anne Burrell - Season 3, Episode 2





Chef Showdown at Le Cirque

Four chefs compete at the legendary New York restaurant Le Cirque for an executive chef position at its sister restaurant Circo in Abu Dhabi. Anne brings in four candidates who must show that they can marry Le Cirque's famed Italian cuisine with the Middle Eastern flavors of Abu Dhabi.





Original Air Date: 08-Aug-2013
